text: Very conveniently located and provides a variety of sushi, don and sashimi to choose from. Chawanmushi is $2 and other stuffs are reasonably priced too.

Highly recommended!

Sushi are all VERY value; $4 for 6 pieces of salmon sushi, $2 for small boxes of sushi etc
Tastes pretty much the same as what you get at Ichiban etc
Staff are always friendly

Food is affordable and delicious however the rolls which they recently introduced I bought 2 which said it contained salmon making however when I took bite out of both of them they were imitation crab . Hopefully they can be mire careful when packing the rolls beside this the place is great
Excellent service! Great food and friendly staff. Will surely come again. Sushi is fresh
